comments: Butler (MIA) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt and makes high-five contact after the release that does not affect Fox's follow-through.
Holmes (SAC) engages and disengages with Adebayo (MIA) during the rebound.
Haliburton (SAC) briefly engages and disengages with Adebayo (MIA) following the rebound.
Hield (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball during the steal.
Herro (MIA) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) legally contests Strus' (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Holmes (SAC) as he engages and disengages with Holmes during the rebound.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Barnes' (SAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Barnes (SAC) at the end of the drive.
Robinson's (MIA) swipes down and makes clean contact to the ball on Fox's (SAC) driving shot attempt.
Robinson (MIA) dislodges the ball from Fox (SAC) while he is airborne during the shot attempt and once Fox returns to the ground he legally regains possession prior to his dribble.
Herro (MIA) does not make contact to Fox's (SAC) arm on his shot near the rim.
Fox (SAC) moves parallel into Butler's (MIA) path and delivers contact and affects his SQBR.
Butler (MIA) slightly extends his forearm as he releases to receive the pass and makes marginal contact with Barnes (SAC).
Adebayo (MIA) places two hands on Barnes (FOX) and does not extend or deliver contact during the pick.
Fox (SAC) makes contact with Robinson's (MIA) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Robinson's (MIA) jump shot fails to hit the rim and neither team has control of the ball when the shot clock expires resulting in a 24 second violation.

Butler (MIA) is drawn into the air and as he returns to the floor, he makes marginal contact with Fox's (SAC) body 
during the pass.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Holmes' (SAC) jump shot attempt.
